Cyclonus picked up the communication from Perceptor and keyed his mic
to answer, "Up to this point the intruder is trapped in the throne
room." he answered as he continued to watch events on the screen. "I
am about to to bring down the security doors to cut off the
possibility of escape."

As he spoke, Cyclonus entered in a series of commands into the
computer, "Keep me apprised of your location Perceptor, and I will
ensure that your path remains open."
